WEBVTT


00:00:42.200 --> 00:00:43.780
- Good!
- Good!

00:01:55.008 --> 00:01:57.728
=The Silent Rift=

00:01:57.984 --> 00:02:00.712
=Episode 11=
(The Variable)

00:02:07.540 --> 00:02:08.120
Zhu.

00:02:29.159 --> 00:02:29.819
Zhu.

00:02:31.539 --> 00:02:33.099
Don't take all that nonsense I said

00:02:34.180 --> 00:02:35.240
to heart.

00:02:36.960 --> 00:02:38.319
You saved me again this time.

00:02:40.740 --> 00:02:43.800
This project I took on
to rebuild Baima Market

00:02:44.520 --> 00:02:46.520
is the biggest deal I've ever done.

00:02:48.319 --> 00:02:51.539
I've sunk all the money
I made before into it.

00:02:52.800 --> 00:02:53.759
But still not enough.

00:02:54.180 --> 00:02:56.300
I've run around to every place
that might lend money.

00:02:59.039 --> 00:03:00.460
If this fails,

00:03:01.659 --> 00:03:02.680
then

00:03:03.659 --> 00:03:04.879
I'll never get back up.

00:03:08.020 --> 00:03:09.520
But this really is a huge project,

00:03:09.819 --> 00:03:11.180
a legitimate and big project.

00:03:14.539 --> 00:03:15.879
Lijun ran the numbers for me.

00:03:16.659 --> 00:03:18.680
Out of this 40-mu market land,

00:03:19.539 --> 00:03:22.740
we can set aside a part to build
dorms as supporting facilities.

00:03:23.379 --> 00:03:26.539
If we sell that part
as commercial housing,

00:03:27.159 --> 00:03:28.680
I don't know about the market,

00:03:29.599 --> 00:03:32.240
but just selling the housing
can make me earn money.

00:03:35.740 --> 00:03:37.020
You'll get an apartment

00:03:37.740 --> 00:03:38.659
when the building's up.

00:03:39.099 --> 00:03:40.159
I wasn't saving you

00:03:41.300 --> 00:03:42.800
or your business, Guangcai.

00:03:43.879 --> 00:03:45.240
That's a human life.

00:03:53.020 --> 00:03:53.960
Think about it.

00:03:54.960 --> 00:03:56.039
I'll be watching you.

00:03:56.900 --> 00:03:58.379
I'll be watching everyone around you.

00:03:59.379 --> 00:04:01.599
Guangcai, if that day really comes,

00:04:03.240 --> 00:04:05.599
I might only bring you
a pair of handcuffs.

00:04:23.936 --> 00:04:27.008
(Beijing, 2004)

00:04:28.379 --> 00:04:31.939
Your Caisheng Group was founded in 1998.

00:04:32.319 --> 00:04:34.319
In 2002, you moved into real estate.

00:04:34.420 --> 00:04:34.939
Okay.

00:04:36.319 --> 00:04:39.699
And immediately after,
you're pivoting to the financial market.

00:04:40.500 --> 00:04:42.980
No wonder people say
your momentum is incredible.

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:45.879
I'm really being pushed beyond my depth.

00:04:47.199 --> 00:04:48.000
But look,

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:50.759
those in real estate
should embrace finance.

00:04:51.439 --> 00:04:53.379
We'll just have to take it step by step.

00:04:53.379 --> 00:04:55.279
Let's make money together.

00:04:56.319 --> 00:04:57.699
Mr. Meng, you're a man of culture.

00:05:00.439 --> 00:05:01.759
This is rare, excellent tea.

00:05:03.540 --> 00:05:05.699
This tea was all prepared by Li.

00:05:05.819 --> 00:05:09.819
I deal with cement and sand every day.
I don't understand this stuff.

00:05:10.100 --> 00:05:12.939
Mr. Meng, you're being far too modest.

00:05:13.100 --> 00:05:16.100
These past months, you've been
in the capital negotiating investments,

00:05:16.259 --> 00:05:19.720
and I see you've managed
everything quite well.

00:05:20.600 --> 00:05:24.279
And having a capable assistant
like Li is truly your good fortune.

00:05:24.939 --> 00:05:27.639
A top-tier university graduate.
That definitely makes a difference.

00:05:27.639 --> 00:05:30.160
Now she's my assistant,
managing even me.

00:05:30.279 --> 00:05:32.879
All my schedules have to go through her.

00:05:34.160 --> 00:05:37.000
Look at you, gone for months,

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:38.500
and you don't even give her a break.

00:05:39.000 --> 00:05:40.939
She needs to date, right?

00:05:43.439 --> 00:05:44.879
Mr. Meng usually works so hard.

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:47.600
We employees can't let our boss down.

00:05:49.220 --> 00:05:52.379
Well said. You have
such a great subordinate.

00:05:52.540 --> 00:05:55.720
We guys here are all green with envy.

00:05:58.639 --> 00:06:00.100
Excuse me, I need to take this call.

00:06:00.339 --> 00:06:00.939
Go ahead.

00:06:00.939 --> 00:06:02.259
Excuse me, duty calls.

00:06:09.000 --> 00:06:10.819
What's wrong? Does it hurt again?

00:06:17.939 --> 00:06:18.439
Here.

00:06:22.319 --> 00:06:23.720
You can't take medicine with tea.

00:06:31.439 --> 00:06:33.100
Taking medicine like this won't work.

00:06:33.339 --> 00:06:34.500
Since we're in Beijing,

00:06:34.639 --> 00:06:37.259
I'll book an appointment
of a good hospital for you.

00:06:38.779 --> 00:06:39.540
Okay.

00:06:40.928 --> 00:06:43.439
(Outpatient)

00:06:43.439 --> 00:06:46.060
I got into fights
when I was young and got injured.

00:06:46.779 --> 00:06:48.279
But I recovered quickly.

00:06:51.720 --> 00:06:55.040
Were there specific symptoms?
Like blood in urine?

00:06:55.439 --> 00:06:57.160
Or constant and severe pain?

00:07:01.160 --> 00:07:06.379
Your shoulder and ribs are cracked.
The worst is the blood in urine.

00:07:10.500 --> 00:07:11.439
In 1988,

00:07:12.100 --> 00:07:13.540
I got hurt in a fight.

00:07:14.540 --> 00:07:15.379
I had blood in urine

00:07:16.720 --> 00:07:18.279
for about two weeks.

00:07:22.100 --> 00:07:23.040
Do you have children?

00:07:26.040 --> 00:07:27.540
Based on the current test results,

00:07:28.139 --> 00:07:30.540
your vas deferens is blocked.

00:07:35.100 --> 00:07:37.139
You understand what I mean, right?

00:07:43.160 --> 00:07:44.319
That means

00:07:46.160 --> 00:07:47.279
I can't father children?

00:07:48.439 --> 00:07:51.220
In term of probability,
it's basically impossible.

00:08:00.540 --> 00:08:02.939
So if I want children, is there a way?

00:08:03.139 --> 00:08:04.540
A minor surgery will do it.

00:08:04.779 --> 00:08:06.819
If you have symptoms,
seek medical help promptly.

00:08:07.160 --> 00:08:10.439
A small problem will become
a big one if you delay treatment.

00:08:14.220 --> 00:08:16.639
Doctor, schedule it for me.
The sooner, the better.

00:08:53.779 --> 00:08:55.039
Why are you back early?

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:57.639
And still wearing these clothes?

00:08:57.639 --> 00:09:00.139
Didn't I give you
new ones when you left?

00:09:00.779 --> 00:09:04.100
Xiaoliang was just saying he wanted
you to take him to the exhibition.

00:09:05.100 --> 00:09:06.399
Today's the last day.

00:09:07.019 --> 00:09:08.000
You could go with him.

00:09:08.279 --> 00:09:09.519
I know little about that.

00:09:10.600 --> 00:09:12.019
I didn't think you'd be back yet,

00:09:12.279 --> 00:09:13.659
so I let Lijun go there with him.

00:09:16.399 --> 00:09:17.840
Don't go out for business tonight.

00:09:18.159 --> 00:09:19.960
I bought your favorite hairy crab.

00:09:30.940 --> 00:09:32.100
I got you a watch.

00:09:32.820 --> 00:09:35.899
Lijun says businessmen from Hong Kong
in China wear this to talk business.

00:09:37.080 --> 00:09:39.320
Image matters in business dealings.

00:09:39.320 --> 00:09:41.080
See if you like it.

00:09:58.100 --> 00:09:59.259
When I was away,

00:10:00.820 --> 00:10:02.139
were you two often together?

00:10:39.820 --> 00:10:41.659
After months of hard work by Mr. Meng,

00:10:42.399 --> 00:10:45.200
we got strong supporters
for the group's transformation.

00:10:45.639 --> 00:10:48.700
But I still suggest
we take things slowly.

00:10:49.600 --> 00:10:52.820
Give subsidiaries
some breathing room to prepare.

00:10:56.500 --> 00:10:57.539
What's wrong, Guangcai?

00:10:57.539 --> 00:10:58.940
Use titles at the company.

00:11:01.460 --> 00:11:02.159
Yes.

00:11:12.820 --> 00:11:16.600
The company's pace won't slow.
You focus on your marketing department.

00:11:18.200 --> 00:11:19.259
Is that clear to everyone?

00:11:19.940 --> 00:11:23.500
Any department holding
the group back will answer to me.

00:11:26.899 --> 00:11:27.820
Back to work.

00:11:44.440 --> 00:11:45.220
Guangcai.

00:11:46.220 --> 00:11:48.720
If I say or do something wrong,

00:11:48.960 --> 00:11:50.320
you can just tell me directly.

00:12:03.759 --> 00:12:05.080
I consider you my buddy.

00:12:08.200 --> 00:12:09.659
I'd die for you.

00:12:12.899 --> 00:12:14.139
How did you treat me?

00:12:37.600 --> 00:12:40.379
Mr. Meng, work is over.
Why are you still here?

00:12:43.639 --> 00:12:44.600
You go ahead.

00:12:46.399 --> 00:12:47.460
I want to stay longer.

00:12:49.320 --> 00:12:53.320
The doctor said your health
can't handle this much drinking.

00:12:57.720 --> 00:12:58.879
Let me take you home.

00:13:18.600 --> 00:13:20.700
Why did you blow up like that today?

00:13:21.320 --> 00:13:22.820
You hurt yourself.

00:13:28.080 --> 00:13:28.720
Does it hurt?

00:13:37.759 --> 00:13:41.500
You seem in low spirits
since returning from your trip.

00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:44.279
Things are different now.

00:13:48.940 --> 00:13:50.600
Now, no matter what happens

00:13:52.580 --> 00:13:53.879
or how I feel,

00:13:55.379 --> 00:13:57.000
I have to

00:13:58.720 --> 00:13:59.659
deal with it alone.

00:14:01.600 --> 00:14:03.000
It's not like before.

00:14:12.019 --> 00:14:13.639
I don't know Mr. Meng you used to be.

00:14:15.100 --> 00:14:16.200
But now,

00:14:17.320 --> 00:14:19.899
the entire Caisheng Group is yours.

00:14:21.460 --> 00:14:25.460
If you want it,
you can achieve anything.

00:14:31.700 --> 00:14:33.779
I'm not that outstanding.

00:14:36.600 --> 00:14:37.639
I'm not successful.

00:14:40.720 --> 00:14:42.080
I can't have

00:14:44.820 --> 00:14:45.820
what I want most.

00:15:01.379 --> 00:15:05.440
No matter what, in my eyes,
you'll always be the best,

00:15:05.720 --> 00:15:06.700
the finest.

00:15:09.940 --> 00:15:11.320
Whatever you choose,

00:15:14.580 --> 00:15:17.639
I'll be with you, okay?

00:15:32.320 --> 00:15:36.096
(Yungui Center)

00:15:47.320 --> 00:15:48.080
You're awake.

00:16:00.500 --> 00:16:01.960
About what happened last night,

00:16:03.580 --> 00:16:05.200
I won't tell anyone.

00:16:07.000 --> 00:16:08.399
Just forget it.

00:16:19.379 --> 00:16:20.159
I'm sorry.

00:16:22.460 --> 00:16:26.340
If you'd like, I can transfer you
to another department.

00:16:33.259 --> 00:16:35.220
If you don't want to step up,

00:16:36.100 --> 00:16:37.519
don't apologize.

00:16:46.899 --> 00:16:48.759
Transferring you to another department

00:16:49.759 --> 00:16:50.759
protects you.

00:16:56.960 --> 00:16:58.580
I want you to stay with me.

00:17:01.200 --> 00:17:03.879
But it'll be tough on you.

00:17:06.039 --> 00:17:07.019
Are you afraid?

00:17:14.960 --> 00:17:16.839
My dad says I've always been brave.

00:17:17.759 --> 00:17:21.019
I saw a bank robbery
as a kid and wasn't scared.

00:17:24.500 --> 00:17:27.799
Staying with you now? Not scared at all.

00:18:18.559 --> 00:18:19.220
Lijun.

00:18:23.339 --> 00:18:24.200
Long time no see.

00:18:27.019 --> 00:18:27.839
Mantang.

00:18:32.759 --> 00:18:36.960
What's up? Lijun,
it's me, Huang Mantang.

00:18:38.839 --> 00:18:39.819
Don't you recognize me?

00:18:40.019 --> 00:18:42.200
I'd know you anywhere.

00:18:44.460 --> 00:18:45.579
When did you get back?

00:18:46.099 --> 00:18:47.920
I missed you guys,

00:18:48.819 --> 00:18:49.839
so I came to see you.

00:18:50.519 --> 00:18:53.500
But this place
wasn't easy to find, Lijun.

00:18:57.380 --> 00:18:58.059
Eaten yet?

00:18:58.059 --> 00:18:58.680
Not yet.

00:18:59.680 --> 00:19:00.259
Get in.

00:19:01.460 --> 00:19:02.180
Welcome dinner.

00:19:02.380 --> 00:19:02.960
Sounds good.

00:19:05.319 --> 00:19:08.579
Lijun, you're doing well!

00:19:10.519 --> 00:19:12.220
Nice, very nice.

00:19:49.640 --> 00:19:51.579
A-Alright, that's enough.

00:19:52.599 --> 00:19:53.259
Eat.

00:19:57.180 --> 00:19:59.839
Buddy, s-s-stop,
I really can't eat anymore.

00:20:02.700 --> 00:20:05.140
Come on, Lijun, let's have a drink.

00:20:05.299 --> 00:20:06.019
I'm driving.

00:20:07.299 --> 00:20:07.799
Okay.

00:20:18.460 --> 00:20:21.339
Lijun, h-honestly,

00:20:23.400 --> 00:20:24.799
great name choice.

00:20:26.180 --> 00:20:28.579
Guangsheng. You've really made it big.

00:20:29.380 --> 00:20:29.960
I...

00:20:29.960 --> 00:20:30.599
Caisheng.

00:20:32.420 --> 00:20:34.579
Yeah, Caisheng.

00:20:34.579 --> 00:20:36.339
Guangcai, the moneybag.

00:20:37.259 --> 00:20:40.500
When I was away,
I always saw it in the papers.

00:20:40.839 --> 00:20:43.680
Remember how fun we were as kids?

00:20:43.880 --> 00:20:46.299
Dazhu always bullied me.

00:20:46.519 --> 00:20:50.380
You and Guangcai always had my back.
Lijun, you're a stand-up guy.

00:20:50.799 --> 00:20:53.319
As soon as I got back, I came to you.

00:21:01.700 --> 00:21:05.759
Lijun, I've been
on my own all these years.

00:21:06.079 --> 00:21:06.940
To be honest,

00:21:09.200 --> 00:21:10.519
I took

00:21:13.759 --> 00:21:14.700
a dark path.

00:21:17.819 --> 00:21:19.519
We've known each other
since we were kids

00:21:19.799 --> 00:21:23.000
and been through a lot together.

00:21:24.259 --> 00:21:26.579
You guys won't just abandon me, right?

00:21:29.680 --> 00:21:30.640
Where are you staying?

00:21:31.880 --> 00:21:33.579
Don't worry about that, Lijun.

00:21:33.579 --> 00:21:34.519
I've got a place.

00:21:34.880 --> 00:21:36.960
I can reach you when I need to.

00:21:38.200 --> 00:21:39.400
Who else have you contacted?

00:21:39.880 --> 00:21:40.579
No one.

00:21:50.460 --> 00:21:51.380
It's good you're back.

00:21:52.220 --> 00:21:53.579
We've come all this way together.

00:21:54.339 --> 00:21:56.700
We are all here.
Who would turn their back on you?

00:21:57.940 --> 00:21:58.839
Understood.

00:22:08.512 --> 00:22:09.420
(Jiao Lijun)

00:22:09.420 --> 00:22:11.519
If you need anything,
just call me anytime.

00:22:15.200 --> 00:22:15.900
Lijun.

00:22:17.099 --> 00:22:21.460
Say hi to Guangcai for me.
I really miss him.

00:22:26.319 --> 00:22:27.880
You finish up. I've got things to do.

00:22:28.700 --> 00:22:29.339
Eat a lot.

00:22:37.920 --> 00:22:40.299
I d-drank too much.

00:23:21.819 --> 00:23:23.059
How did he find you?

00:23:23.180 --> 00:23:24.900
Caisheng's influence is huge now.

00:23:26.000 --> 00:23:29.839
There are newspaper and TV interviews
every day. Finding us isn't hard.

00:23:30.579 --> 00:23:33.680
Oh, right. Huang Mantang
asked me to give you a message.

00:23:34.319 --> 00:23:35.420
He said he misses you.

00:23:39.440 --> 00:23:41.408
The true concern is
being targeted by a thief.

00:23:43.259 --> 00:23:45.000
He doesn't just want money, does he?

00:23:45.259 --> 00:23:46.759
I wish it were just about money.

00:23:47.920 --> 00:23:49.559
But now, our operations are so big,

00:23:51.680 --> 00:23:52.900
and so many eyes are on us.

00:23:54.180 --> 00:23:56.559
He ran off back then,
and we couldn't find him.

00:23:57.460 --> 00:24:01.180
He comes back now.
Some money probably won't cut it.

00:24:08.880 --> 00:24:10.200
This day is bound to come.

00:24:13.420 --> 00:24:15.099
We shouldn't have gone easy on him.

00:24:19.180 --> 00:24:20.220
Keep an eye on him.

00:24:28.299 --> 00:24:29.000
Guangcai.

00:24:29.200 --> 00:24:29.700
What?

00:24:29.700 --> 00:24:30.200
He...

00:24:30.799 --> 00:24:31.579
Anything else?

00:24:35.936 --> 00:24:36.448
(Cash Book)

00:24:38.299 --> 00:24:39.180
We'll talk later.

00:24:53.559 --> 00:24:54.079
Hello.

00:24:58.960 --> 00:24:59.839
How's the baby?

00:25:01.960 --> 00:25:05.339
You just had the baby.
Don't push yourself to go out.

00:25:07.579 --> 00:25:11.019
I'm at the office
to handle an urgent thing.

00:25:12.000 --> 00:25:13.440
I'll go see you and the baby later.

00:25:15.059 --> 00:25:16.799
Okay.

00:25:32.059 --> 00:25:34.380
Lijun, this afternoon, you and Dazhu...

00:25:38.259 --> 00:25:39.180
Meng Guangcai!

00:25:40.720 --> 00:25:42.579
You think you're fooling anyone?

00:25:42.839 --> 00:25:45.079
What did you promise Qin
when you married her?

00:25:45.880 --> 00:25:48.680
How much hardship
has she endured with you?

00:25:48.839 --> 00:25:49.839
How could you do this?

00:25:50.299 --> 00:25:52.680
Now, with a little money
and the kid grown up,

00:25:52.680 --> 00:25:54.059
you can't keep it in your pants?

00:25:54.339 --> 00:25:55.839
Who are you to lecture me?

00:25:58.819 --> 00:26:01.559
I just want to carry on my family line!
What's wrong with that?

00:26:01.579 --> 00:26:04.579
Aren't Qin and Xiaoliang enough for you?

00:26:07.180 --> 00:26:09.960
I knew long ago
Xiaoliang wasn't my biological son.

00:26:12.539 --> 00:26:15.299
The son I have raised for 15 years
isn't my biological son.

00:26:16.900 --> 00:26:18.799
Who could put up with that?

00:26:19.940 --> 00:26:21.299
I did!

00:26:23.180 --> 00:26:24.140
Guangcai, you...

00:26:27.079 --> 00:26:28.259
You've already stopped hiding

00:26:29.720 --> 00:26:31.579
the thing between you two, haven't you?

00:26:32.839 --> 00:26:33.559
I...

00:26:35.019 --> 00:26:36.380
Is Meng Xiaoliang your son?

00:26:37.559 --> 00:26:38.200
Tell me.

00:26:39.220 --> 00:26:41.319
Tell me, is Meng Xiaoliang your son?

00:26:42.200 --> 00:26:43.440
Answer me!

00:26:43.920 --> 00:26:45.000
Tell me!

00:26:45.000 --> 00:26:45.559
No.

00:26:47.819 --> 00:26:49.140
You're lying to me!

00:27:01.319 --> 00:27:02.579
Meng Guangcai!

00:27:06.380 --> 00:27:07.079
He...

00:27:09.000 --> 00:27:09.880
What?

00:27:21.339 --> 00:27:23.000
We've been good buddies for 30 years.

00:27:25.200 --> 00:27:26.400
How have I treated you?

00:27:27.900 --> 00:27:29.819
And this is how you
treat a buddy, right?

00:27:31.559 --> 00:27:33.259
You come here today to question me?

00:27:34.259 --> 00:27:35.799
I'll tell you straight.

00:27:38.140 --> 00:27:42.460
I never intended to hide
Li Fen and that child from anyone.

00:27:54.579 --> 00:27:55.680
Guangcai.

00:28:42.339 --> 00:28:43.380
Mine.

00:28:52.880 --> 00:28:53.559
Lijun!

00:29:29.079 --> 00:29:29.579
I...

00:29:41.559 --> 00:29:42.420
Mine.

00:30:11.460 --> 00:30:12.460
What's going on?

00:30:17.460 --> 00:30:18.380
No need for this.

00:30:20.839 --> 00:30:22.299
Say it if you have an issue with me.

00:30:25.079 --> 00:30:26.299
No, not at all.

00:30:28.140 --> 00:30:28.799
Wait.

00:30:56.079 --> 00:30:57.140
You investigated me?

00:31:04.140 --> 00:31:05.680
You investigated me?

00:31:10.880 --> 00:31:12.079
I could pretend I didn't know

00:31:14.079 --> 00:31:15.440
the thing between you two.

00:31:15.960 --> 00:31:17.599
But now, you have a child together.

00:31:19.880 --> 00:31:21.200
I can't play dumb anymore.

00:31:23.759 --> 00:31:25.299
I never intended to hide it from you.

00:31:26.759 --> 00:31:27.819
So be it if you know.

00:31:29.680 --> 00:31:31.220
This is the child I had with Li Fen.

00:31:33.640 --> 00:31:35.500
Are you planning
to share this home with her?

00:31:37.140 --> 00:31:37.960
Don't worry.

00:31:40.059 --> 00:31:42.140
The position
of the Caisheng Group Chairman's wife

00:31:43.180 --> 00:31:44.079
is only yours.

00:31:44.640 --> 00:31:45.799
She won't fight you for it.

00:31:46.140 --> 00:31:47.460
What exactly are you doing?

00:31:56.920 --> 00:31:57.880
What am I doing?

00:32:01.200 --> 00:32:02.700
I've raised another man's son.

00:32:05.440 --> 00:32:06.579
It's eating me up inside.

00:32:10.839 --> 00:32:13.000
All I want is a child of my own.

00:32:14.000 --> 00:32:15.059
Am I wrong?

00:32:22.460 --> 00:32:23.460
Jiao Lijun

00:32:25.180 --> 00:32:28.000
should be kicked out
of Caisheng and get lost.

00:32:31.900 --> 00:32:33.460
He thought he could steal you away.

00:32:34.559 --> 00:32:35.559
No way back then.

00:32:37.500 --> 00:32:38.700
No way now.

00:32:40.460 --> 00:32:42.059
Make him give up on that idea.

00:32:55.880 --> 00:32:57.180
The woman I love most

00:32:59.339 --> 00:33:00.640
and my best buddy

00:33:02.180 --> 00:33:03.579
ganged up to make a fool out of me.

00:33:15.000 --> 00:33:15.839
Xue Qin,

00:33:18.460 --> 00:33:19.900
I just want to ask you one thing.

00:33:23.440 --> 00:33:24.720
Did you ever love me?

00:34:07.968 --> 00:34:11.552
(Higher Education Admission Letter)

00:34:13.699 --> 00:34:16.719
I got in! I really got in!

00:34:17.079 --> 00:34:23.199
You're the first from our village to get
into the county teachers' college.

00:34:23.199 --> 00:34:27.008
(Xue Qin)

00:35:07.460 --> 00:35:08.099
Laosi.

00:35:08.719 --> 00:35:09.360
Zhu.

00:35:10.300 --> 00:35:12.099
The place you picked is out of the way.

00:35:13.860 --> 00:35:17.000
Wearing gold-rimmed glasses now.

00:35:17.260 --> 00:35:18.519
That chain looks good too.

00:35:19.340 --> 00:35:20.360
I made a little money.

00:35:20.360 --> 00:35:21.920
You must have struck it rich.

00:35:22.699 --> 00:35:26.119
Treating me to dinner
today to tell me that?

00:35:26.360 --> 00:35:29.199
No, just a few small dishes.
You call this rich?

00:35:29.639 --> 00:35:30.440
I missed you.

00:35:30.559 --> 00:35:31.320
Oh, come on.

00:35:31.320 --> 00:35:32.619
So secretive. Something's up.

00:35:33.619 --> 00:35:34.800
Have some water.

00:35:38.159 --> 00:35:39.019
Spit it out.

00:35:39.619 --> 00:35:41.900
Nothing much.
I just wanted to get together.

00:35:42.340 --> 00:35:44.139
Just say it. Don't I know you?

00:35:44.619 --> 00:35:48.800
I know you're stubborn.

00:35:49.139 --> 00:35:53.219
For over ten years,
you've been stuck on this 6.10 case.

00:35:53.639 --> 00:35:56.159
Can't you just let it go?

00:35:58.820 --> 00:35:59.579
Go on.

00:35:59.820 --> 00:36:01.219
That's it. Just eat.

00:36:04.000 --> 00:36:06.280
It's been ages since we
sat down for a meal together.

00:36:12.699 --> 00:36:14.320
At a dinner I attended recently,

00:36:16.320 --> 00:36:17.679
there was a new face.

00:36:17.820 --> 00:36:21.880
He got drunk and bragged,
mentioning the Beiyan robbery.

00:36:24.500 --> 00:36:27.119
I vaguely felt
it was related to the 6.10 case.

00:36:27.119 --> 00:36:28.099
But I'm not sure.

00:36:32.900 --> 00:36:33.840
What did he look like?

00:36:34.219 --> 00:36:36.300
Not tall, a bit dark.

00:36:37.000 --> 00:36:40.460
He sounded like a local from Beiyan.

00:36:41.960 --> 00:36:43.139
I don't know much else.

00:36:44.360 --> 00:36:46.380
What's his name? Where does he live?

00:36:46.380 --> 00:36:47.260
What business?

00:36:47.260 --> 00:36:48.860
Tell me the specific details.

00:36:49.920 --> 00:36:53.420
I just met him once.
How could I know all that?

00:36:53.619 --> 00:36:54.860
And taking out a notebook?

00:36:55.000 --> 00:36:56.460
Zhu, let me look into it, okay?

00:36:56.460 --> 00:36:58.619
Can you put the notebook down first?

00:36:58.619 --> 00:36:59.776
Don't look into it, Laosi.

00:37:00.679 --> 00:37:02.139
You're not a cop anymore.

00:37:02.460 --> 00:37:04.340
If you have a lead,
tell me. I'll investigate.

00:37:04.599 --> 00:37:05.840
Just stay out of it.

00:37:06.179 --> 00:37:08.019
Wait, you are investigating?

00:37:09.000 --> 00:37:11.119
The man was just drunk and bragging.

00:37:11.119 --> 00:37:13.639
You want to drag him
to the police station?

00:37:14.559 --> 00:37:16.639
If word gets out, how can I do business?

00:37:16.639 --> 00:37:18.900
How will I get by? Give it a rest.

00:37:18.900 --> 00:37:21.019
Put the notebook down and eat.

00:37:24.420 --> 00:37:25.179
Alright.

00:37:26.960 --> 00:37:27.639
Laosi.

00:37:30.159 --> 00:37:33.099
Since I have nothing much on today,

00:37:34.119 --> 00:37:35.360
tell me.

00:37:36.659 --> 00:37:38.464
All these years,
you've been so secretive.

00:37:39.249 --> 00:37:41.420
What kind of business are you in?

00:37:42.139 --> 00:37:42.860
Tell me.

00:37:44.880 --> 00:37:45.860
Small business.

00:37:47.159 --> 00:37:49.199
Making enough to eat.

00:37:50.420 --> 00:37:52.679
You do your thing. I do mine.

00:37:54.179 --> 00:37:57.460
I'll tell you if I hear anything.
Stop asking all the time.

00:38:00.420 --> 00:38:01.619
I'm here for the food anyway.

00:38:01.619 --> 00:38:02.519
Right.

00:38:03.460 --> 00:38:07.019
By the way, don't tell
Liu Unity about this.

00:38:07.019 --> 00:38:07.840
Why not?

00:38:08.500 --> 00:38:11.860
He's naggy. I get annoyed
whenever he talks to me.

00:38:15.008 --> 00:38:18.639
(Serve the people)

00:38:18.639 --> 00:38:19.320
Zhu.

00:38:20.219 --> 00:38:20.860
Laoer.

00:38:22.559 --> 00:38:23.599
Got your clothes changed?

00:38:24.079 --> 00:38:24.960
Wait for me a bit.

00:38:24.960 --> 00:38:27.119
I'll get changed,
and we'll go out for a walk.

00:38:27.119 --> 00:38:27.920
Not today.

00:38:29.460 --> 00:38:30.599
Did you forget it?

00:38:30.599 --> 00:38:32.860
We just agreed last week
to visit Lin Shan together.

00:38:34.159 --> 00:38:34.900
You forgot it?

00:38:34.960 --> 00:38:35.619
I forgot.

00:38:35.760 --> 00:38:36.719
Your memory's terrible.

00:38:36.719 --> 00:38:40.659
Qianqian's homeroom teacher asked me
to come today to discuss something.

00:38:40.860 --> 00:38:43.519
Alright, you go ahead first.
I'll head over once I'm done.

00:38:43.659 --> 00:38:44.599
Okay.

00:38:46.420 --> 00:38:47.380
Don't worry.

00:39:00.579 --> 00:39:02.300
It's said this guy owes a lot of money.

00:39:04.219 --> 00:39:07.380
The key is that he's a drug user too.
Many people are looking for him.

00:39:08.719 --> 00:39:11.260
I've heard he's in this ruin,
but I don't know exactly where.

00:39:11.880 --> 00:39:12.900
We need to search.

00:39:14.679 --> 00:39:16.119
This place looks like a maze.

00:39:17.420 --> 00:39:18.300
I'd never find

00:39:19.699 --> 00:39:21.139
this spot before you mentioned it.

00:39:21.360 --> 00:39:24.719
Yeah, this slum area
is basically empty, so he hides here.

00:39:24.719 --> 00:39:26.260
This is a good place to hide.

00:39:27.880 --> 00:39:28.400
Laosi.

00:39:29.860 --> 00:39:32.559
When was the last time
you saw that person?

00:39:32.960 --> 00:39:34.219
Just two days before we met up.

00:39:34.219 --> 00:39:36.179
There! Hurry!

00:40:04.659 --> 00:40:05.760
What are you doing?

00:40:05.940 --> 00:40:09.000
Sir, did you see a man run past here?

00:40:09.159 --> 00:40:10.059
No, no.

00:40:10.900 --> 00:40:13.400
May I ask, do you live here alone?

00:40:13.400 --> 00:40:14.820
I live here with my wife.

00:40:18.099 --> 00:40:19.119
Sorry to bother you.

00:40:24.820 --> 00:40:25.619
Go check over there.

00:40:43.019 --> 00:40:43.579
This way.

00:41:08.219 --> 00:41:10.519
I'll chase from this side.
You cut him off over there.

00:41:10.519 --> 00:41:11.659
Okay. Be careful.

00:42:47.219 --> 00:42:48.079
Du Ming!

00:42:49.119 --> 00:42:49.960
Du Ming!

00:42:56.340 --> 00:42:56.940
Du Ming!

00:42:58.679 --> 00:42:59.519
Du Ming!

00:43:05.380 --> 00:43:06.079
Du Ming!

00:43:06.880 --> 00:43:07.559
Du Ming!

00:43:17.019 --> 00:43:17.780
Du Ming!

00:43:20.460 --> 00:43:21.360
Du Ming!

00:43:23.900 --> 00:43:24.880
Du Ming!

00:43:29.800 --> 00:43:31.099
Du Ming!

00:43:41.540 --> 00:43:46.564
=The Silent Rift=